    "covariates": "Tested: concomitant medications, AGE, SEX, WT, HT, ethnicity, ideal body mass (IBM), BSA, CLcr, ALAT, ASAT, alkaline phosphatase (ALP), gamma-GT, albumin, bilirubin, urea, creatinine, hemoglobin Included: BSA, ASAT, ALP,WT",
    "observations": "Validation of the model against data from 17 patients shows significant overpredictions. Concentrations within the population largely fell outside the therapeutic window, which may impact the estimation of the pharmacokinetic parameters given the non-linearity of PHT elimination",
